 Safaricom held its fourth regional summit of Blaze BYOB Season Two on November 11 at Machakos Stadium, Machakos county. The
summit was pegged on this year’s theme of GRIT (Greatness Requires
Internal Toughness). It trained youths to tackle challenges in entrepreneurship and business head-on, and persevere
through them. Mentors at the summit included fashion blogger Nick Ondu, video producer J Blessing, comedian Njugush and content developer Abel Mutua. 
There were special performances by artistes Nyashinski, King Kaka, Khaligraph, Femi One and Timmy T-Dat. Previous regional summits were in Meru, Nakuru and Eldoret, reaching 25,000 Blazers.